         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">28/8/94. ¶  ¶ On close examination I find, dear Mr Maiden, must be as a variety of Andropogon nervosus (as as you say Ischaemum laxum) which therefore is new to N.S.W. ¶  It is a short-spiked form, an...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.08.28a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Maiden</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Library, Royal Botanic Gardens, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28/8/94.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On close examination I find, dear Mr Maiden, must be as a variety of <name key="Andropogon%20nervosus">Andropogon nervosus</name> (as as you say <name key="Ischaemum%20laxum">Ischaemum laxum</name>) which therefore is new to N.S.W.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M was sent a 'bot spec' from the Technological Museum, Sydney on 7 August</seg>
                     <seg style=""> 1894 ('Parcels posted and forwarded' entry no. 43 for 1894, Powerhouse Museum Sydney, MRS 105). </seg>
                  </p>
               </note> It is a short-spiked form, and differs also in some other respects but so far as I can make out from your specimen, not <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>specifically.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With best remembrance your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I have returned the whole specimen by this mail, but you might let me have a little of it for the sake of locality.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Andropogon%20nervosus">Andropogon nervosus</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Ischaemum%20laxum">Ischaemum laxum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
